signal_description:
Count the number of case_id records in the defaultview-57 table where the event_name column does NOT contain any of the values: 
'Update PR Delivery Date', 
'Reactivate PR Item',
'Update PR Material',
'Update PR Quantity',
'Update PR Net Price',
'Update PO Vendor',
'Update PO Currency',
'Update PO Payment Terms',
'Send PO Overdue Note',
'Dun Order Confirmation',
'Send Purchase Order Update',
'Reactivate PO Item',
'Update PO Item Material',
'Update PO Item Quantity',
'Update PO Item Net Price',
'Update PO Item Plant',
'Update PO Confirmed Delivery Date',
'Reverse Goods Receipt',
'Reverse Invoice',
'Set Payment Block',
'Remove Payment Block',
'Change Payment Block',
'Update Invoice Payment Method',
'Update Invoice Payment Terms'
AND the event_name column contains the value 'Create Goods Receipt'. 
Divide this count by the total count of records where event_name is 'Create Goods Receipt' and multiply by 100 to get the percentage.
